channel.title: Crashing Your Computer
channel.description:
Hey I need to crash our other computer.. The format option and stuff ain't working. So I tried a batch file to delete C: :P but didn't work. Does anyone know a quick easy way to crash a computer or have a batch file or something to delete the files so it will crash?
Thanks

item.title: Crashing Your Computer
item.dc:creator: @Rictoo Rictoo
item.description:
@Rictoo wrote:

Put in the XP cd, go to Recovery Prompt, if you have no password for admin, leave the admin password blank and press enter. Then type ‘format C:’ and have fun =/
